Text.string: Quit killing my family, you bastard!
We're gonna get you for that!
But we had you SO outnumbered!
We won't run! We won't run!
Don't let that pet piss on our stuff!
You're not as tough as us!
Please don't call your mech, please don't call your mech!
Oooh, look at me, I got competent military training!
AH! Sorry, I was blinded by your hair!
Ah, crap! That guy looks good!
Where'd you get them fancy clothes, pretty boy?!
Whew, I thought we were screwed!
Awwww, come on back, Vault Thief!
Fine! Just leave! I don't care!
[frustration grunt] Why does this take so long?!
You're gonna DIE! (beat) In a second!
Open wide! Got a rocket for ya!
Eat lead or laser or whatever!
Gahh! Get it! Get it! Get iiit!
They can shoot through that thing!
What the fresh crap is this?
Maybe we should worship HER instead!
I'll join YOUR cult, just don't hurt me!
Guess you can't win a fair fight!
No one said anything about mechs!
I'm not trained for this! I'm not trained for anything!
Where the hell did she get that?
Ah, crap! She brought a mech!
There's HOW MANY of these jerks now?!
Don't be fooled! It's a decoy!
Just more of you to kill!
[rapid] Please don't punch me! Please don't punch me!
Think she's got names for all those fists?
Come out, come out, wherever you are!
What the--? Where did they go?!
I sure hope they don't sneak attack me!
She's coming in for a landing!
Ugh! Now we've gotta deal with RAKKS?!
Crap, crap, crap, get away! Get away!
Somebody get this thing off of me!
Don't worry, my cousin's a veterinarian!
Put that thing in a kill shelter!
Yo, fam! Kill the freak beast!
We'll meet again at the Great Vault!
[taunting laughter] We ain't done with you yet!
Awww, did the Vault Thief get a boo-boo?!
We'll do that again if we have to!
I see the Great Vault! It's so beautiful!
The family is gonna rip you apart!
For the glory of the Twin Gods!
Bring it! Bring it on, Vault Thief!
Come on, Vault Thief! Whatchu got?
For the glory of the Twin Gods!
We are the CHILDREN OF THE VAULT!
When in doubt, chop it out!
Sucks to be you, Vault Thief!
Coming for that scalp, Vault Thief!
You're as dumb as you look.
Where do you think YOU'RE going?
I could drive circles around you!
I guess I'll just hop out then!
Looks like this is my stop!
I'm the one! I'm the one who got you!
Say hello to the champ! That's me!
I got 'em! I got the Vault Thief!
Help us out, we're getting creamed!
Hell yeah -- let's chop the Vault Thief!
Get in there and meet your murder quotas!
Finally! Let the blood party begin!
More fam. Now it is ON!
Family reunion! Let's chop this thief!
